{
  "id": "5c358f6f5667170017ec8038",
  "title": "わかりやすさの責任",
  "created": 1547014002,
  "updated": 1547014437,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c358f6f5667170017ec8038",
      "text": "わかりやすさの責任",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014002,
      "updated": 1547014004
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358f74aff09e000090f492",
      "text": "\t[掘り下げ]で書いた、「賢い人はわかりやすく説明できる、はfalse」の続き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014004,
      "updated": 1547014082
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359032aff09e000090f49f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014194,
      "updated": 1547014194
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358f78aff09e000090f494",
      "text": "\tAさんが解説をし、Cさんがそれを理解できなかった、という事象が発生した場合",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014009,
      "updated": 1547014101
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358fd4aff09e000090f497",
      "text": "\t\tAさんが適切な説明をしているがCさんにそれを受け止められるだけの知識がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014101,
      "updated": 1547014128
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358ff0aff09e000090f498",
      "text": "\t\tAさんの説明が適切でない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014128,
      "updated": 1547014133
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358ff4aff09e000090f499",
      "text": "\tのどちらであるのかは、この条件だけからはわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014133,
      "updated": 1547014141
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359030aff09e000090f49e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014193,
      "updated": 1547014193
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358ffdaff09e000090f49a",
      "text": "\t他責では物事が改善しないので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014142,
      "updated": 1547014154
    },
    {
      "id": "5c35900aaff09e000090f49b",
      "text": "\t\tAさんは、自分の説明が悪かったと考えて、説明を改善する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014155,
      "updated": 1547014166
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359015aff09e000090f49c",
      "text": "\t\tCさんは、自分の知識が不足していると考えて、知識を習得する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014166,
      "updated": 1547014179
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359022aff09e000090f49d",
      "text": "\tが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014179,
      "updated": 1547014278
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359085aff09e000090f4a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014278,
      "updated": 1547014278
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359085aff09e000090f4a1",
      "text": "\tAさんは質問されれば掘り下げて説明することができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014278,
      "updated": 1547014288
    },
    {
      "id": "5c35908faff09e000090f4a2",
      "text": "\tAさんはCさんの内部の知識状況を知り得ない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014288,
      "updated": 1547014298
    },
    {
      "id": "5c359099aff09e000090f4a3",
      "text": "\tだから物事を進めるには",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014298,
      "updated": 1547014348
    },
    {
      "id": "5c3590ccaff09e000090f4a4",
      "text": "\t\tCさんが何がわからないかを表明する #質問責任",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014348,
      "updated": 1547014437
    },
    {
      "id": "5c3590ceaff09e000090f4a5",
      "text": "\t\tAさんが「Cさんが何をわからないのか」を問いかける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014351,
      "updated": 1547014367
    },
    {
      "id": "5c3590ceaff09e000090f4a6",
      "text": "\tなどの必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014351,
      "updated": 1547014371
    },
    {
      "id": "5c358f75aff09e000090f493",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014005,
      "updated": 1547014372
    },
    {
      "id": "5c3590e4aff09e000090f4a8",
      "text": "\tまあこれはリソースが無限にある状況で「Cさんが理解する」を達成する方法論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014372,
      "updated": 1547014414
    },
    {
      "id": "5c35910daff09e000090f4aa",
      "text": "\t実際にはAさんのリソースは有限だから、Cさんを見捨てて終了になることも多い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014414,
      "updated": 1547014428
    },
    {
      "id": "5c3590e6aff09e000090f4a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547014375,
      "updated": 1547014375
    }
  ]
}